{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act38side", "eventName": "揭幕者們", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "PV-6", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "“復仇於我”", "storyInfo": "柳德米拉回到營地，得知索默爾尚未回來。心懷愧疚的她一路查到港口，發現了失蹤的卡車與車廂內走私的武器。為了不讓卡車互助會陷入更大的麻煩，柳德米拉點了一把火。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "56_g9_truckcamp", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=2>1100年11月6日    3:20 P.M.</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_only_medium", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "實在不好意思，助理先生，讓您白跑一趟了。", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_701_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她沒有告訴你們她去哪裡了？", "name": "法官助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_701_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有，但、但是請您轉告拉維妮婭法官，伊雷妮有在認真調查她拜託的事情。", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊雷妮剛回到營地，就讓我們對互助會名下的卡車進行自查了，她這時出去應該也是為了找車禍的線索——", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_701_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別緊張。我不是為這件事而來的。", "name": "法官助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_701_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？那——欸，柳德米拉，你知道伊雷妮去哪裡了嗎？", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回營地怎麼還偷偷摸摸的，差點都沒注意到你……", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你衣服怎麼還破了？和別人打架了？", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "摔了一跤。", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#3$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_701_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你就是柳德米拉？", "name": "法官助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_701_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_701_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我有東西要給你。", "name": "法官助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_701_1#1$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "本來是應該由伊雷妮統一處理的，她不在，直接交到你手裡也剛剛好。", "name": "法官助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_701_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是？", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_701_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "市民告知函和身分證明文件。", "name": "法官助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_701_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你通過了市政廳與法院的背景審查，你的市民積分也夠了……", "name": "法官助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_701_1#1$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從今天起，你就是新沃爾西尼的合法市民、卡車工會的正式在籍司機了，享有《新都市管理法案》所規定的一切權益。", "name": "法官助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_701_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，終於終於！", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "柳德米拉，你昨天那一頓加鹽汽水請太早了！", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_701_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很意外嗎？我們知道你的——呃，特殊之處。", "name": "法官助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_701_1#1$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還是需要定期接受礦石病檢查，如果感染情況惡化的話，我們會重新評估對你的處理方案。", "name": "法官助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_701_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡車工會在這座城市的地位很特殊，以你的情況，本來確實很難通過背景審查……", "name": "法官助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_701_1#1$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊雷妮這段時間為這件事沒少往市政廳和法院跑，最後她親自為你做了風險擔保，許多司機都跟著在申請文件上簽了名。", "name": "法官助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_701_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#4$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀，柳德米拉，別用這樣的眼神看著我嘛。總不能讓你平時白請我們吃東西喝東西吧。", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_701_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "柳德米拉？", "name": "法官助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_701_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您別怪她，她一向話不多……我當時拿到告知函和身分證明文件的時候可比她失態多了。", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_701_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能理解，根據資料顯示，當初收養你的舅舅被捲入幫派鬥爭，全家都被滅門……其實大家都差不多……", "name": "法官助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_701_1#1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "新沃爾西尼建成之後，許許多多曾受到家族壓迫的敘拉古人都趕來了這裡，取得新的身分，擺脫家族的影響……", "name": "法官助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_701_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "甚至有不少家族成員，也透過這種形式脫離了家族。", "name": "法官助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_701_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在新沃爾西尼，我們每個人都擁有擺脫過去、擁抱新生活的權利。", "name": "法官助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_701_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恭喜你，柳德米拉。", "name": "法官助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_701_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "柳德米拉看著手裡的市民告知函和身分證明文件，沉默著。"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "MusicVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.1, "fillto": 0.1, "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.1, "fillto": 0.1, "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "56_g2_newvolsiniistreet_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“不期而會”，我沒什麼文化，但我知道這是一個好詞……你不覺得它就是在講我們這些人嗎？", "name": "索默爾"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就當是倒楣蛋們不期而會了吧，哈哈。", "name": "索默爾"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊雷妮那丫頭總說，再倒楣的人也會被生活眷顧的，只是會晚一點。", "name": "索默爾"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "56_g9_truckcamp", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "MusicVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是對倒楣蛋的眷顧嗎……", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#3$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-200,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "柳德米拉，你到底怎麼了？", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "索默爾有沒有回來？", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有，他不是從昨晚開始到今天都休息嘛，可能是去挑送小古莉的狂歡節禮物了吧。", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別幫他隱瞞了，魯傑羅。", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道你們的事情……我昨晚就在索默爾的車上。", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "昨晚的那場車禍？", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，是我們的車。", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天哪——", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……看你的反應，索默爾沒回來。快想想他可能去哪裡了。", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#7$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們昨晚應該原定在第三碼頭附近的載具檢修站交貨，我們有時候也會選威尼斯載具公司名下的幾個廢棄倉庫……", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都找過了。", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#5$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我回了撞車的地方，現場已經被封鎖，索默爾和車都不知所蹤，我也去了你剛剛說的那些地方……都沒有。", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#5$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#5$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我怎麼能就那麼走掉呢，該死的，如果我沒有被那個狼崽子吸引，說不定……", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#7$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "柳德米拉……", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我再去找！", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#7$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "-500,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "56_g11_newvolsiniipier", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.7, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_craneworking", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=2>1100年11月7日    2:30 P.M.</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_only_medium", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 2.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#5$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……只剩下這裡了。", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#5$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "柳德米拉站在貨櫃之間，抬眼看向面前繁忙的港口。"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "整整一天過去了，她找了她能找的所有地方，但一無所獲。"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她可以在天災肆虐的切爾諾伯格穿行，在混亂的戰場帶隊準確鎖定敵人，但她如今卻找不到一個普普通通的卡車司機。"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "柳德米拉覺得有人跟自己開了一個玩笑，她突然有些無力。"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_696_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_701_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是說，現在就把那些花車開走？", "name": "港口工人"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對啊，都已經組裝完成了，全部運往拓展地塊，那是狂歡節當晚巡遊的起點。", "name": "調度員"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這我知道，我的意思是，不是本來安排在晚上嗎？", "name": "港口工人"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你沒看見剛剛那場暴雨嗎？突如其來的。新沃爾西尼很少有這樣的壞天氣，鬼知道今天還會不會再下雨……", "name": "調度員"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "十幾輛巨型花車，動起來那麼大的陣仗，真要碰上剛剛那樣的大雨，就得進行道路管制，會有很多不必要的麻煩。", "name": "調度員"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說得也是。", "name": "港口工人"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "趁著雨停了，儘快吧。", "name": "調度員"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，沿途會經過不少地方，記得幫每輛花車都蓋上帆布，市政廳的意思，巡遊開始前，花車造型都得保持神秘。", "name": "調度員"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，我去召集人手。", "name": "港口工人"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "250,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-200,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果索默爾只能原路返回，想要在這忙碌的港口藏起一輛車，難道說……", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#5$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-350,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "false", "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "新沃爾西尼港的一角，十幾輛工程吊車撐起巨大的帆布，在露天處憑空創造出一座封閉的迷宮。"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "十幾隻造型奇特的巨大野獸沉寂在帆布之下，在狂歡節復活之前，這裡就是它們的墓園。"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "柳德米拉就這麼經過它們，她沒有心情去研究這些怪傢伙，她徑直走到隊伍的末尾，然後停了下來——"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是一隻巨狼。它巨量的擬真皮毛覆蓋住了身下卡車的車廂。尾巴剛好垂在了車廂那醒目的凹陷和劃痕上。"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巨狼張開血盆大口無聲地向前方怒吼，所有不可告人的秘密都藏在它的身下。"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_trnpndor"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "柳德米拉拉開了貨廂的門，眼前是堆滿的黑色輪胎，以及……"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是……", "name": "柳德米拉"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "MusicVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.1, "fillto": 0.1, "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.1, "fillto": 0.1, "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "56_g2_newvolsiniistreet_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你幫威尼斯運的是什麼貨？", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1547_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天晚上是一批輪胎。", "name": "索默爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1547_1#1$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "基本都是載具生產會用到的耗材，源石引擎、鋼件、合金之類的，有時候也有一些凍鱗凍肉或酒精藥品……", "name": "索默爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1547_1#1$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這種事情在敘拉古的其他城市很常見，家族的商品基本都不走正常的報關流程，能省很大一筆稅。只不過在新沃爾西尼——", "name": "索默爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1547_1#1$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "56_g11_newvolsiniipier", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "MusicVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "柳德米拉抽出匕首，沿著她剛剛看見的裂口，劃開了厚實的輪胎表面，露出裡面的東西。"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "銃械、法杖、制式弩箭，甚至還有源石炸藥……", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#6$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "索默爾，你真蠢啊，你知道自己在運的，是這樣的“商品”嗎？", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#6$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*烏薩斯粗口*，事情竟然比走私輪胎，誤撞了代理市長還要複雜！等等，有人……", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#7$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-200,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.2, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "應該就是這裡了。", "name": "粗嗓子"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "甘比諾，你這邊我那邊，動作快一點。", "name": "粗嗓子"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡彭，你有想過嗎，要是真的找到了，怎麼向小威尼斯交代我們是從哪裡得到線索的？", "name": "大嗓門"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總不能說是拉普蘭德告訴我們的吧？", "name": "大嗓門"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我更關心的是，那個瘋子是怎麼知道索默爾把卡車藏在新沃爾西尼港的……", "name": "粗嗓子"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以及，她到底想做什麼？", "name": "粗嗓子"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了，想這些沒有意義，開工吧——等等，外面好像有條子，躲一躲！", "name": "大嗓門"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前輩，我是諾埃米。", "name": "甜甜的聲音"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前輩，你那邊有什麼發現了嗎？", "name": "甜甜的聲音"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從來不喝咖啡，好苦。", "name": "甜甜的聲音"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼啊，前輩你別打岔了！我知道肇事車輛可能藏在哪裡了，你快點過來！", "name": "甜甜的聲音"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對，就在新沃爾西尼港的西邊，停放花車的地方！", "name": "甜甜的聲音"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_truckengine", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.5, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，港口的人已經開始……", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#4$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "柳德米拉聽見工程吊車的機械臂扯落帆布的聲響，以及前方車輛陸續發動的聲響。"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "家族的人和警察都在不遠處，這輛花車、花車下的秘密、索默爾，還有那些卡車司機的“新生活”很快就將暴露在天光之下。"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*烏薩斯粗口*！", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#7$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "柳德米拉的手拂過自己的身側，她觸摸到了一片濕潤。那是一份摺疊起來的文件，證明自己已經成為那些愚蠢的傢伙的一員。"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "應該是剛剛跑來港口的時候被雨淋濕了，離開營地的時候，她甚至沒來得及將它放回自己的帳篷。"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "深秋時節，又淋了一場雨，現在回過神來，還真是冷，柳德米拉心想。"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是能生堆火取暖就好了。"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_1002_nsabr_2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "char_1502_crowns", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_iceforest_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$distressed_intro", "key": "$distressed_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兄弟，看看雪地上的這堆篝火。曾經，它可以點燃感染者的憤怒，點燃整合運動的理想，燒遍整個烏薩斯。", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "char_1502_crowns"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是現在，它只夠你和我取暖。", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "char_1502_crowns"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_wilderness_m", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“先學會點火吧，燒掉這棟房子，和這裡面的一切，讓其他人再也找不到我們。”", "x": 100.0, "y": 300.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“柳德米拉，火會隱藏一切。”", "x": 100.0, "y": 300.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_burn", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$firestorm"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.4, "r": 1.0, "g": 0.6, "b": 0.3, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_wilderness_m", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.7, "yScale": 1.7, "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_churchfire", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.3, "amount": 0.0}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "56_i03", "fadetime": 1.0, "xScale": 1.2, "yScale": 1.2, "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 45.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "柳德米拉站在不遠處的陰影裡，沉默地看著火焰從車廂燃起，爬升，很快吞沒了整隻巨狼。"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "火可以點燃憤怒，點燃理想，火也可以掩埋一切。"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而自己的煙霧可以隱藏火焰。在其他人發現之前，她足以讓火勢擴大到無法被熄滅。"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "柳德米拉"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，真倒楣啊。", "name": "柳德米拉"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}